  "decision_conditions": [
    "The proposed three-storey side extension, in combination with the additional storey at roof level, would result in an overly dominant and obtrusive form of development that would fail to be subservient to the host property and would be harmful to the character and appearance of the original dwelling and the terrace of which it forms part of.&amp;nbsp; As such, the proposal is considered to be of poor design that fails to meet the requirements of The London Plan (2021) policies D3 (Optimising site capacity through the design-led approach), D4 (Delivering good design), and policies LP1 (Design Quality and Local Character) and LP17 (Housing Design Standards) of the &lt;br&gt;Hackney Local Plan LP33 (2020) and Hackney&#x27;s Residential Alterations and Extension SPD (2009)."
